  <thing id="rauBishFea" name="Fear Aura" description="A bishop&apos;s eerie, fishlike appearance evokes feelings of unsettling fear in foes within a 30-foot radius. The bishop can use this aura as a free action, and any creature within this area must succeed at a Will save or become shaken for 5d6 rounds. A creature that succeeds at its save is immune to the bishop&apos;s aura for 24 hours. The save DC is Wisdom-based." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Foes within radius are affected by the {i}fear{/i} spell.">
    <usesource source="PathShStar"/>
