  <thing id="rauChrRcMe" name="Racial Memory" description="As a full-round action, any caulborn within 300 feet of a chrestomath may access the latter&apos;s racial memory to gain half the chrestomath&apos;s Knowledge skill bonus as a bonus on its own Knowledge check. In addition, the chrestomath instantly acquires any piece of information learned by any caulborn that comes within 300 feet of it. This information may then be shared by any other caulborn and chrestomaths with 300 feet." compset="RaceSpec">
