  <thing id="rauFacFear" name="Fear Aura" description="Each creature within a 30-foot radius that sees the fachen must succeed at a DC 15 Will save or be paralyzed by fear for 1d4 rounds. A creature that successfully saves is not subject to the same fachen&apos;s fear aura for 24 hours. This is a paralysis effect and a mind-affecting fear effect. The save DC is Charisma-based." compset="RaceSpec" summary="Foes within radius are affected by the {i}fear{/i} spell.">
