  <thing id="rauMezMrpB" name="Morphic Body" description="A mezlan can assume the appearance of any Medium or Small creature (other than creatures with the elemental, incorporeal, or swarm subtypes-the body assumed must be solid). The mezlan&apos;s creature type doesn&apos;t change in this new form and it gains none of the mimicked creature&apos;s special abilities; the transformation is cosmetic only. In these other forms, the mezlan retains all of its normal statistics and abilities as depicted above. Though this ability only affects the mezlan&apos;s outward image, it is a transmutation effect." compset="RaceSpec">
